Package voicesplitting.voice.hmm

Provides the HMM-based voice splitting model which is the main focus of this project.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HmmVoiceSplittingModel
    An HmmVoiceSplittingModel is the model that performs voice separation as described in the paper.
    HmmVoiceSplittingModelParameters
    An HmmVoiceSplittingModelParameters contains the parameters to use for an HmmVoiceSplittingModel.
    HmmVoiceSplittingModelState
    An HmmVoiceSplittingModelState is used to store an HmmVoiceSplittingModel's current state.
    HmmVoiceSplittingModelTester
    An HmmVoiceSplittingModelTester contains the HmmVoiceSplittingModelTester.main(String[]) method used to train and test the HmmVoiceSplittingModel class from the command line.
    HmmVoiceSplittingModelTesterReturn
    An HmmVoiceSplittingModelTesterReturn is the return object for a HmmVoiceSplittingModelTester thread.

Package voicesplitting.voice.hmm Description

Provides the HMM-based voice splitting model which is the main focus of this project.

This package contains both the model itself, and classes which can be used to train and test the model, which should be run using the main method in HmmVoiceSplittingModelTester.
